The adapted portions include the compact/expanded HUD structure, configurable
element ordering, progress-bar presentation, activity-line conventions,
threshold colors, and Full/Essential/Minimal configuration concepts. Codex
rollout parsing, session discovery, tmux lifecycle management, Codex plugin
integration, and Codex-specific telemetry normalization are Codex HUD work.
